    3.2 When using this APP, users need to disclose some information as required, including but not limited to contact phone number, delivery address, etc., as well as some necessary information required by third-party payment institutions to enjoy Internet payment services, which include but are not limited to: real name, contact address, email address and contact phone number, etc. You shall ensure that such information is true, accurate, valid and complete when provided, and shall update such information in a timely manner according to actual circumstances or the requirements of this APP. Any restrictions or losses incurred when receiving services from this APP due to incomplete, untrue information disclosure or untimely information updates shall be borne by you independently. In addition to necessary information, you also have the right to decide to disclose some other information.
