    4.3 Users are obligated to ensure the security of their passwords and accounts. Any losses or damages caused by all activities conducted by users using such passwords and accounts shall be borne entirely by the users themselves, and this APP shall not bear any responsibility.
    4.4 Users shall not lend the account registered on this APP to others for use; otherwise, the user shall bear all responsibilities arising therefrom and shall be jointly and severally liable with the actual user.
    4.5 If a user finds that their account has been used without authorization or any other security issues occur, they shall immediately change the account password and keep it properly. If necessary, please notify this APP; otherwise, all responsibilities arising therefrom shall be borne by the user themselves. This APP shall not be liable for unauthorized use of the account due to hacking or the user's negligence in keeping it secure.
